me">SysvSharedMemory</a></span>        instance now; previously, a <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.resource.php" class="type resource" style="color:#EAB766">resource</a></span> was expected.       </td>      </tr>     </tbody>       </table>   </div>  <div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.shm-put-var-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><ul class="simplelist">    <li><span class="function">{@link shm_get_var()} - Returns a variable from shared memory</span></li>    <li><span class="function">{@link shm_has_var()} - Check whether a specific entry exists</span></li>   </ul>   </div></div>
